<project name="Drugref.org"
  url="http://www.drugref.org/">
  <p>
    Drugref.org is a collaborative attempt at creating and maintaining an
    independent free pharmaceutical reference database.
  </p>
  <p>
    The principles include
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>continuous peer review of all information</li>
    <li>independence of industry</li>
    <li>independence from funding related constraints</li>
    <li>independence from countries, health systems, and languages</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    This project depends on active community contributions. Anybody
    with a medical, pharmaceutical or biochemical degree is welcome
    to contribute.
  </p>
</project>
